Create a new human. :param height: :param shoe_size: :param altitude_in_meter: :param altitude_in_millimeter: :param fingers_count: :param hair_count: :param is_happy: :param name: :param eyes_color: :param organization_id: One-Of (‘project_identifier’): at most one of ‘project_id’, ‘organization_id’ could be set. :param project_id: One-Of (‘project_identifier’): at most one of ‘project_id’, ‘organization_id’ could be set. :return: Human

    altitude_in_meter=1,
    altitude_in_millimeter=1,
    fingers_count=1,
    hair_count=1,
    is_happy=False,
    name="example",
)
